OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy, with outbreaks of rain
OL,6,Fat times. The rain will be mainly
OL,7,Flight and patchy, with eastern areas
OL,8,Fmost prone to catching some damp
OL,9,Fweather. The best of any sunnier
OL,10,Fbreaks are expected over west
OL,11,FCornwall. Feeling colder than Thursday.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FIt will remain mostly cloudy
OL,14,Fthis evening and overnight, with
OL,15,Ffurther rain at times, mainly in the
OL,16,Feast. Turning chilly where any cloud
OL,17,Fbreaks occur, with a few fog patches.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
