OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FA largely cloudy morning,
OL,6,Fwith some light rain in places,
OL,7,Fnotably in the east. The cloud may
OL,8,Fbreak during the afternoon to allow
OL,9,Fsome sunshine through. Feeling a
OL,10,Flittle milder.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FThe
OL,13,Fcloudy theme will continue. It will be
OL,14,Fmostly dry, but some showery rain may
OL,15,Fbe possible at times. Feeling mild
OL,16,Fwhere the cloud breaks and the sun
OL,17,Fcomes out.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
